‫בתאריך יום ה׳, 15 ביוני 2023 ב-10:39 מאת ‪Amir E. Aharoni‬‏ &lt;‪
amir.aharoni@mail.huji.ac.il‬‏&gt;:‬

<div class="quoted-switch"><a style="font-weight:normal" href="#">...</a></div><div
class="quoted-text quoted-text-0">  The problem is valid, but probably not a blocker.

 If the current content is valid in that script, it can be approved,
 especially if a reasonable converter can be made.

